CustomField.description: Stores the size/volume of input data for the task/query that's being measured (if applicable). For example if you are measuring a named query execution you could place here the number of characters in the SOQL string.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Stores the size/volume of input data for the task/query that's being measured (if applicable). For example if you are measuring a named query execution you could place here the number of characters in the SOQL string.
CustomField.label: Input Data Volume
